channel.title: How to change names
channel.description: hi i downloaded server from moparscape server downloads but i need to know how i change names like in quest tab at top of client inlog name and for pk points can somebody help me?

item.title: How to change names
item.dc:creator: @totalystylin1 totalystylin1
item.description:
@totalystylin1 wrote:

pray4urlife:

Open your source folder up then hit ctrl f then put the name of the server and it will come up with all the place it is in then open it like one will be client.java so open it then hit ctrl f again and search for it then replace it with your server name. Compile, Done!

^^^
